	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001126_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>10 Soho Square</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>2<hi rend="sup">d</hi> Nov<hi rend="sup">r</hi></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Shaw</persName>
<lb/>You are quite 
<lb/>right about the 
<lb/>balls. I ought 
<lb/>to have said 
<lb/>the ball was 
<lb/>an eight to the 
<lb/>pound ball or 
<lb/>two ounces<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001126_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>As some more may 
<lb/>be printed off 
<lb/>yet I have ordered 
<lb/>the phrase to be 
<lb/>changed to a two 
<lb/>ounce ball. When 
<lb/>you mentioned it 
<lb/>I looked at another 
<lb/>place where the 
<lb/>same gun &amp; ball 
<lb/>is spoken of 
<lb/>properly<reg>.</reg></p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001126_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">I am glad that you 
<lb/>are pleased with 
<lb/>it. I have written 
<lb/>your name in 
<lb/>a copy, and one 
<lb/>will come to the 
<lb/>society on the 
<lb/>9<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> for the Library 
<lb/>if <choice><sic>admissable</sic><corr>admissible</corr></choice>. </p>
<lb/><p>The large map 
<lb/>is at <placeName>Birmingham</placeName>
<lb/>but I wrote off for 
<lb/>it this morning 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001126_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>and it will be 
<lb/>here in good time 
<lb/>for you. Thanks 
<lb/>for the ticket 
<lb/>you sent me<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I go down to <placeName>Rugeley</placeName> on <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hursday 
<lb/>but will come up 
<lb/>so as to be at the 
<lb/>meeting on Monday 
<lb/>the 9<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi><reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am ever</p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/>yours</p> 
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
